{"tid":1742983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[罷搭成績表] 10月党鐵本地客量繼續下跌 俾9月跌14%","createTime":"2019-11-21T04:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T08:13:20.000Z","uid":26602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d7a3bf5a410dd35b41c023f05571ffc8424358","tid":1742983,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/corporate/investor/patronage.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcorporate%2Finvestor%2Fpatronage.php&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=89dada6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/corporate/investor/patronage.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2EcReD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2EcReD.png&h=4581c176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10月份党鐵本地綫總乘客量為<strong>108,456,000人次</strong><br />\n<br />\n比9月份126,948,000再跌18,492,000人次, 約14.5% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkr6VGA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnkr6VGA.png&h=653fc714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要繼續罷搭, 等佢跌破一億人次大關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c81a1339c442b3b3ed05f6e2cf9715ca84f4ee","tid":1742983,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:19:32.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-u